(Kassel u.a.: Bärenreiter, 2011) viii, 258p</li>
<li><b>Leahy, Anne</b>:
<i>J. S. Bach's
'Leipzig Chorale' Preludes: Music, Text, Theology</i>, ed.
Robin A. Leaver (Lanham: Scarecrow Press, 2011). xxviii, 297p</li>
<li><b>Rose, Stephen</b>:
The Musician in Literature in the Age of Bach&nbsp;(Cambridge
University Press, 2011) ix, 237p</li>
